Attribution
-----------
This mod adapts code from Superb Warfare (https://github.com/Mercurows/SuperbWarfare),
Copyright (C) its authors (Atsuishio, Roki27, Light_Quanta), licensed GPL-3.0.
Reused: the kill-message queue and the entry slide/fade animation timing
(KillMessageHandler, KillMessageOverlay, LivingKillRecord) and the attacker
resolution in the kill path (LivingEventHandler), ported from Kotlin/Forge 1.20.1
to Java/NeoForge 1.21.1 and stripped of Superb Warfare's guns, vehicles, dog tags,
custom damage types, and all art assets.
